  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 400f (200c).",
    "char the eggplants over an open flame or on a grill until the skin is blistered and blackened.",
    "peel the eggplants and dice them into 1-inch cubes.",
    "in a large saucepan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "add the garlic, ginger, cumin, coriander, salt, and pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the eggplant cubes and smoked paprika, and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "transfer the mixture to a baking dish and cover with foil.",
    "bake for 30 minutes.",
    "remove the foil and bake for an additional 15 minutes.",
    "garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
